      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still smelling new and showing zero signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This is a collector-grade example that needs nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
