      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to work for you! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition\u2014it\u2019s seen some miles and shows a bit of character through normal wear and tear, but it\u2019s a dependable performer that still has plenty of life left. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a solid, functional car at a great price point without the showroom sticker!",
